{"id":6841,"date":"2023-11-05T20:30:49","date_gmt":"2023-11-05T12:30:49","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.acclime.com\/?page_id=6841"},"modified":"2023-12-12T15:31:27","modified_gmt":"2023-12-12T07:31:27","slug":"microsoft-dynamics-erp-crm-solutions","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.acclime.com\/services\/microsoft-dynamics-erp-crm-solutions\/","title":{"rendered":"Microsoft Dynamics 365, ERP &#038; CRM solutions for APAC and Greater China"},"content":{"rendered":"<h1>Microsoft Dynamics 365, ERP &amp; CRM solutions for APAC and Greater China<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h1>\n<div>\n<p>Integrate your organisation into APAC and Greater China with customised enterprise resource planning (ERP) and customer relationship management (CRM) solutions.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<ul>\n<li>\n        <a href=\"\/contact\/\">Talk to an expert<\/a>\n    <\/li>\n<li>\n        <a href=\"#more\">Learn more<\/a>\n    <\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/acclime_web_image_14.jpg\" alt=\"Enterprise solutions for APAC and Greater China\"><br \/>\n<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/MS-partner-logos.svg\" alt=\"\"><br \/>\n<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/acclime-dots-grid.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<h2>Integrate your organisation with custom solutions<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h2>\n<div>\n<p>As a Microsoft Certified Partner, Acclime leverages the power of Dynamics 365 Business Central to help you implement ERP and CRM solutions into your operations. You will gain greater visibility and control over your finances, while also improving customer engagement and loyalty.<\/p>\n<p>Enterprise solutions connects to a range of external systems, and our in-house application team is experienced at developing interfaces with <strong>SAP, Dynamics NAV, Dynamics AX, Web-based ordering systems, 3PL, and cloud-based systems<\/strong>. The end result for your operations is increased speed and enhanced collaboration among the different stakeholders of your APAC business.\u00a0<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/expertise.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<h4>Trust our expertise<\/h4>\n<div>\n<p>We are an official Microsoft Partner for implementation of ERP and CRM solutions built on Microsoft platforms and guarantee quality work.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/capital-usd.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<h4>Reduce IT investment<\/h4>\n<div>\n<p>We implement ERP\u2019s that help client to digitally connect their subsidiaries, avoiding heavy IT investment since we take care of everything on the backend.<\/p><\/div>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/commitment.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<h4>Integrate functions<\/h4>\n<div>\n<p>We create a dynamic synergy with all our teams working on the corporate services we provide for you, especially on the accounting and trade side.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h6><span class=\"uk-icon uk-icon-image dot-alignment\" style=\"background-image: url(\/wp-content\/uploads\/dot.svg);\"><\/span> China enterprise solutions<\/h6>\n<h2>Streamline your operations with Dynamics 365 ERP modules and functionalities<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h2>\n<div>\n<div>\n<h3 class=\"uk-margin-small-bottom uk-h4\"><span class=\"uk-icon uk-icon-image\" style=\"background-image: url('\/wp-content\/uploads\/dot.svg'); margin-bottom: 4px; width: 16px;\"><\/span> Accounting<\/h3>\n<ul class=\"uk-margin-small-top\">\n<li>General ledger, P&amp;L, balance sheets<\/li>\n<li>Budgets, group reporting<\/li>\n<li>Consolidated accounts<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<h3 class=\"uk-margin-small-bottom uk-h4\"><span class=\"uk-icon uk-icon-image\" style=\"background-image: url('\/wp-content\/uploads\/dot.svg'); margin-bottom: 4px; width: 16px;\"><\/span> Treasury<\/h3>\n<ul class=\"uk-margin-small-top\">\n<li>Payments and receipts<\/li>\n<li>Online approvals<\/li>\n<li>AR &amp; AP management<\/li>\n<li>Payroll &amp; taxation<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/circle.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<div>\n<div>\n<h3 class=\"uk-margin-small-bottom uk-h4\"><span class=\"uk-icon uk-icon-image\" style=\"background-image: url('\/wp-content\/uploads\/dot.svg'); margin-bottom: 4px; width: 16px;\"><\/span> Trade and inventory<\/h3>\n<ul class=\"uk-margin-small-top\">\n<li>Product, customer and vendor management<\/li>\n<li>Invoices, orders and shipping<\/li>\n<li>Inventory monitoring and management <\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<h3 class=\"uk-margin-small-bottom uk-h4\"><span class=\"uk-icon uk-icon-image\" style=\"background-image: url('\/wp-content\/uploads\/dot.svg'); margin-bottom: 4px; width: 16px;\"><\/span> Manufacturing<\/h3>\n<ul class=\"uk-margin-small-top\">\n<li>Supply and capacity management <\/li>\n<li>Detailed bills of materials<\/li>\n<li>Assembly-to-order support<\/li>\n<li>Improved production order processes<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<h2>Optimise your customer engagement with Microsoft Dynamics CRM<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h2>\n<div>\n<p>Adding Microsoft&rsquo;s CRM to Dynamics 365 Business Central allows you to create an integrated solution that&rsquo;s available on premises or through the cloud. Dynamics 365 CRM is a flexible sales and marketing platform that can improve how you engage and do business with your customers.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>Features include tools for planning and launching marketing campaigns, managing leads, and creating quotations, orders, and invoices.&nbsp;<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/acclime-triangle-curve.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<hr>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/acclime_web_images_33.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<h2>Combining Dynamics 365 ERP and CRM enhances your productivity and efficiency<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h2>\n<div>\n<p>Benefits for your organisation include:&nbsp;<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Global access to shared information&nbsp;<\/li>\n<li>Accurate and timely data&nbsp;<\/li>\n<li>Easy data analysis and reporting&nbsp;<\/li>\n<li>Customised access and approval rights&nbsp;<\/li>\n<li>Automated communication flows&nbsp;<\/li>\n<li>Integration of Acclime compliance, finance, and trade services&nbsp;<\/li>\n<li>Cloud-based versatility and security <\/li>\n<li>Cost synergies&nbsp;<\/li>\n<li>Outsourced ERP and IT management&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div>\n<h6><span class=\"uk-icon uk-icon-image dot-alignment\" style=\"background-image: url('\/wp-content\/uploads\/dot.svg');\"><\/span> Custom data visualisation<\/h6>\n<h2>Customise how you see your data<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h2>\n<div>\n<p>Leverage the power of <strong>Dynamics 365 Business Central Integrations<\/strong> together with <strong>Power BI<\/strong> visualisation tools to get the view of your business you need.<\/p>\n<p>Power BI is interactive data visualisation and reporting software with a primary focus on business intelligence. It is part of the Microsoft Power Platform. Our team of certified Microsoft developers work alongside our corporate services teams, who are specialised in ERP applications, to create truly customised platforms.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<h6><span class=\"uk-icon uk-icon-image dot-alignment\" style=\"background-image: url(\/wp-content\/uploads\/dot.svg);\"><\/span> The Acclime difference<\/h6>\n<h2>Why choose the Acclime Enterprise solutions<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/capital.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<h4>Lower fixed costs<\/h4>\n<div>\n<p>There are no hardware or software setup or maintenance fees and no annual ERP license. Server hosting, ERP maintenance, and system updates are covered by Acclime and Microsoft.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/minimise.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<h4>Lower variable costs<\/h4>\n<div>\n<p>You do not need to hire IT and ERP team specialists. We take care of the system and its infrastructure for you.\u00a0<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/compliance-services.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<h4>Integrated with our trade and supply chain services<\/h4>\n<div>\n<p>Integration with our trade and supply chain services enables streamlined production and delivery throughout Greater China and the world.\u00a0<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/flexible-expand.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<h4>Access to Acclime&#8217;s corporate services<\/h4>\n<div>\n<p>Access to the Acclime group\u2019s wide range of integrated business services throughout Asia.\u00a0\u00a0<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h5>Ready to get started?<\/h5>\n<h2>Discover how we can build your custom enterprise solutions in APAC<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h2>\n<p>\n    <a href=\"\/contact\/\">Talk to an expert<\/a>\n<\/p>\n<p><!--more--><br \/>\n<!-- {\"type\":\"layout\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"section\",\"props\":{\"animation\":\"fade\",\"css\":\".el-section {\\n    background-image: linear-gradient(to top,#f9f9f9,transparent);\\n}\",\"image\":\"wp-content\\\/uploads\\\/dotted-grid-medium.svg\",\"image_effect\":\"parallax\",\"image_height\":\"300\",\"image_parallax_bgx\":\"-300,-300\",\"image_position\":\"center-left\",\"media_visibility\":\"xl\",\"padding\":\"large\",\"style\":\"default\",\"title_breakpoint\":\"xl\",\"title_position\":\"top-left\",\"title_rotation\":\"left\",\"vertical_align\":\"middle\",\"width\":\"default\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"row\",\"props\":{\"layout\":\"2-3,1-3\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"column\",\"props\":{\"image_position\":\"center-center\",\"position_sticky_breakpoint\":\"m\",\"vertical_align\":\"middle\",\"width_medium\":\"2-3\"},\"children\":[